Interface CellRange<C extends Cell>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<C>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SSCellRange 

    public interface CellRange<C extends Cell>
extends java.lang.Iterable<C>
    Represents a rectangular region of a Sheet(表示图纸的矩形区域)

        int size()
        Gets the number of cells in this range.(获取此范围中的单元格数。)
        Returns:
        height * width (高度 * 宽度)

      • getReferenceText

        java.lang.String getReferenceText()
        Returns:
        the text format of this range. Single cell ranges are formatted like single cell references (e.g. 'A1' instead of 'A1:A1').(此范围的文本格式。单个单元格范围的格式类似于单个单元格引用（例如“A1”而不是“A1：A1”）。)

      • getTopLeftCell

        C getTopLeftCell()
        Returns:
        the cell at relative coordinates (0,0). Never null.(相对坐标（0，0）处的单元格。从不为空。)

      • getCell

        C getCell(int relativeRowIndex,
          int relativeColumnIndex)
        Parameters:
        relativeRowIndex - must be between 0 and height-1(relativeRowIndex -必须介于0和height-1之间)
        relativeColumnIndex - must be between 0 and width-1(relativeColumnIndex -必须介于0和宽度-1之间)
        Returns:
        the cell at the specified coordinates. Never null.(指定坐标处的单元格。从不为空。)

      • getFlattenedCells

        C[] getFlattenedCells()
        Returns:
        a flattened array of all the cells in this CellRange(此CellRange中所有单元格的扁平阵列)

      • getCells

        C[][] getCells()
        Returns:
        a 2-D array of all the cells in this CellRange. The first array dimension is the row index (values 0...height-1) and the second dimension is the column index (values 0...width-1)(此CellRange中所有单元的2-D阵列。第一个数组维度是行索引（值0. height-1），第二维是列索引（值0.宽度-1）)

      • iterator

        java.util.Iterator<C> iterator()
        Specified by:
        iterator in interface java.lang.Iterable<C extends Cell>(界面中的迭代器java.lang.Iterable)
        Returns:
        an Iterator over all cells in this range. Iteration starts with all cells in the first row followed by all cells in the next row, etc.(该范围内所有单元格的迭代器。迭代从第一行中的所有单元格开始，然后是下一行中的所有单元格，等等。)
